com.cubeia.firebase.bot.ai

Class AbstractAI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cubeia.firebase.bot.ai.AbstractAI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AI, StateAI
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicAI, MttAI

    public abstract class AbstractAI
extends Object
implements AI
    Functionality common to all abstract AI implementation. The Basic AI and MTT AI both provides game specific bots with abstract and common functionality, but they both share some logic which is contained in this class.
    Author:
    Fredrik
